Detailed Description

CbmiRangeProvider is the provider to retrieve and manipulate the Cbmi values of the sim (GSM 11.11 V8.2.0 10.3.28). An instance of this class is part of the Apoxi Data Control. A pointer to this provider can be retrieved from the main provider via the id:

c_cbmi_range_provider_id

Following column ids are defined: c_cbmi_range_low_id :NumberType c_cbmi_range_high_id :NumberType

NOTE: Please do not instantiate this class.
